<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0">
  <title>에브리북클럽</title>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="../_ui_include/web_head.js"></script><!-- //Include: head -->
</head>
<body>
  <div id="wrap" class="wrap">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../_ui_include/web_header.js"></script>
    <div id="container" class="container">
      
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#none" class="home"><span class="hidden ">HOME</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="#none">앱 다운로드</a></li>
          <li class="current"><a href="#none">이용방법</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
  
      <div class="sc-sub-area v2">
        <h2 class="sc-sub-tit">이용방법</h2>
        <p>에브리북클럽 디지털 콘텐츠<br><b>이렇게 이용할 수 있어요!</b></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="section">
        <div class="tablet-box num-type">
          <div class="swiper-container">
            <ul class="swiper-wrapper">
              <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="swiper-content">
                  <div class="swiper-img-box">
                    <img src="../../resources/img/web/app_use_img01.png" alt="">
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-txt">
                    <strong>앱 로그인 화면</strong>
                    <p>APP 다운로드 후 학습을 진행할 학생을 선택해 주세요.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="swiper-content">
                  <div class="swiper-img-box">
                    <img src="../../resources/img/web/app_use_img02.png" alt="">
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-txt">
                    <strong>에브리북클럽 메인</strong>
                    <p>이 달의 도서 4권과 학습 진도율, 학습 리포트, 나의 스티커, 출석표를 확인할 수 있어요.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="swiper-content">
                  <div class="swiper-img-box">
                    <img src="../../resources/img/web/app_use_img03.png" alt="">
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-txt">
                    <strong>독서 및 독서 확인 학습</strong>
                    <p>눈으로 읽는 이북은 물론 오디오북, 독후 확인 게임을 통해 즐겁게 책을 읽을 수 있어요.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="swiper-content">
                  <div class="swiper-img-box">
                    <img src="../../resources/img/web/app_use_img04.png" alt="">
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-txt">
                    <strong>문해력 게임 진행</strong>
                    <p>문해력 게임과 글쓰기를 통해 독서에 나온 어휘들을 완벽하게 습득할 수 있어요.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="swiper-slide">
                <div class="swiper-content">
                  <div class="swiper-img-box">
                    <img src="../../resources/img/web/app_use_img05.png" alt="">
                  </div>
                  <div class="swiper-txt">
                    <strong>성장맵 확인</strong>
                    <p>독서 진도율에 따라 변화하는 나만의 성장맵을 확인해 보세요.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-button-wrap">
            <button type="button" class="swiper-button-prev"><span class="hidden ">이전</span></button>
            <button type="button" class="swiper-button-next"><span class="hidden ">다음</span></button>
          </div>
          <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- bottom banner -->
      <div class="btm-banner">
        <div class="in">
          <p>우리아이 독서습관 지금 바로 시작해보세요!</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn lg primary">에브리북클럽 시작하기</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!--// bottom banner -->
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../_ui_include/footer.js"></script>
    <script>
      var swiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container', { 
          slidesPerView: 1,
          spaceBetween: 0,
          autoplay: true,
          delay: 2500,
          centeredSlides: true,
          loop : false,
          loopAdditionalSlides : 1, 
          pagination: { 
            el: ".swiper-pagination",
            clickable: true,  
            renderBullet: function(index, className) {
              return '<li class="'+className+'"><span>' + 0+(index+1) +'</span></li>';
            }
          },
          navigation: {
            nextEl: ".swiper-button-next", 
            prevEl: ".swiper-button-prev",
          },
        });
    </script>
  </div>
</body>
</html>